00:33:25,400 --> 00:33:28,120
this will be a massacre at sea.

589
00:33:31,040 --> 00:33:33,840
Then I'll go ask Translator Luo again.

590
00:33:33,840 --> 00:33:35,480
After all, he's Chinese.

591
00:33:35,480 --> 00:33:37,400
He wouldn't just stand by

592
00:33:37,400 --> 00:33:38,930
when someone's in trouble.

593
00:33:39,800 --> 00:33:40,680
Bingchen,

594
00:33:42,040 --> 00:33:43,170
I'm counting on you.

595
00:33:44,000 --> 00:33:44,640
Degong.

596
00:33:46,320 --> 00:33:47,600
After the autopsy,

597
00:33:47,600 --> 00:33:49,400
what conclusion did they reach?

598
00:33:51,000 --> 00:33:52,930
They determined the time of death.

599
00:33:53,520 --> 00:33:55,360
13 hours ago,

600
00:33:55,880 --> 00:33:57,480
between 4 and 5 PM yesterday.

601
00:33:57,720 --> 00:34:00,000
That's when you were at the hospital.

602
00:34:00,880 --> 00:34:01,600
What else?

603
00:34:03,000 --> 00:34:04,080
Also,

604
00:34:05,160 --> 00:34:07,040
there was no trace of smoke inhalation

605
00:34:07,040 --> 00:34:09,199
in his tracheal walls.

606
00:34:09,199 --> 00:34:10,280
This means

607
00:34:10,760 --> 00:34:12,800
he had already stopped breathing

608
00:34:13,239 --> 00:34:15,239
before the motorcycle caught fire.

609
00:34:15,760 --> 00:34:17,889
That's why he didn't inhale any smoke.

610
00:34:20,920 --> 00:34:21,880
There's more.

611
00:34:21,880 --> 00:34:23,040
Don't panic. What else?

612
00:34:23,040 --> 00:34:23,639
Also,

613
00:34:27,159 --> 00:34:28,120
they said

614
00:34:28,960 --> 00:34:30,679
they found alcohol in his stomach.

615
00:34:30,679 --> 00:34:32,540
Which means he had been drinking.

616
00:34:33,639 --> 00:34:34,320
Go on.

617
00:34:34,320 --> 00:34:35,239
What else?

618
00:34:40,360 --> 00:34:43,120
They said he died from asphyxiation

619
00:34:43,400 --> 00:34:45,330
due to a broken cervical vertebra.

620
00:34:47,320 --> 00:34:48,719
But the doctor said

621
00:34:49,400 --> 00:34:51,719
it could have been broken in the fall.

622
00:34:53,800 --> 00:34:54,560
That's all.

623
00:34:56,719 --> 00:34:57,920
You're a doctor too.

624
00:34:57,920 --> 00:34:59,980
What do you think of this conclusion?

625
00:35:00,480 --> 00:35:01,280
Don't worry,

626
00:35:01,680 --> 00:35:03,410
there's another possibility.

627
00:35:03,720 --> 00:35:04,520
Suppose Inoue

628
00:35:04,520 --> 00:35:06,080
landed headfirst

629
00:35:06,080 --> 00:35:07,610
when he fell from the cliff.

630
00:35:08,000 --> 00:35:08,600
It's possible that

631
00:35:08,600 --> 00:35:10,320
his neck broke,

632
00:35:10,320 --> 00:35:11,780
causing him to suffocate.

633
00:35:12,400 --> 00:35:13,800
If he died first,

634
00:35:13,800 --> 00:35:15,560
and the motorcycle caught fire afterward,

635
00:35:15,560 --> 00:35:16,600
that would explain

636
00:35:16,600 --> 00:35:17,800
why there was no smoke

637
00:35:17,800 --> 00:35:18,720
in his airways.

638
00:35:21,800 --> 00:35:22,240
This conclusion

639
00:35:22,240 --> 00:35:23,640
is very favorable for us.

640
00:35:27,720 --> 00:35:28,960
Oshima Hiroshi knows

641
00:35:29,360 --> 00:35:30,920
that Inoue came to the hospital

642
00:35:30,920 --> 00:35:32,320
after being bitten.

643
00:35:33,320 --> 00:35:35,160
And his wound

644
00:35:35,560 --> 00:35:37,360
was treated by me.

645
00:35:39,400 --> 00:35:40,960
When you were treating his wound,

646
00:35:40,960 --> 00:35:42,800
was anyone else present?

647
00:35:44,320 --> 00:35:45,400
Dr. Ozu.

648
00:35:48,400 --> 00:35:49,360
Tang Ju'er,

649
00:35:49,880 --> 00:35:50,960
from now on,

650
00:35:51,240 --> 00:35:52,400
I hope you can calmly

651
00:35:52,400 --> 00:35:53,680
listen to what I'm about to say.

652
00:35:53,680 --> 00:35:54,840
Can you do that?

653
00:35:57,400 --> 00:35:58,560
Early tomorrow morning,

654
00:35:58,560 --> 00:36:00,200
the special police unit will launch

655
00:36:00,200 --> 00:36:01,930
a large-scale investigation.

656
00:36:02,320 --> 00:36:03,040
Soon,

657
00:36:03,240 --> 00:36:04,000
they will find

658
00:36:04,000 --> 00:36:05,400
the person who bit Inoue.

659
00:36:05,560 --> 00:36:06,480
Then they'll discover

660
00:36:06,480 --> 00:36:08,600
that Inoue arrived at the base hospital

661
00:36:08,600 --> 00:36:09,280
at a time

662
00:36:09,280 --> 00:36:11,400
around 4 or 5 in the afternoon,

663
00:36:11,400 --> 00:36:13,280
which is exactly when we were at the hospital.

664
00:36:13,280 --> 00:36:14,520
Our time at the hospital

665
00:36:14,520 --> 00:36:16,760
coincides perfectly with Inoue's time of death.

666
00:36:16,760 --> 00:36:18,000
This will become the focus

667
00:36:18,000 --> 00:36:19,320
of Oshima Hiroshi's investigation.

668
00:36:19,320 --> 00:36:20,360
What should we do?

669
00:36:21,400 --> 00:36:22,400
Don't panic.

670
00:36:22,880 --> 00:36:24,400
They will soon discover

671
00:36:24,400 --> 00:36:26,040
that Inoue Kamakura was alive

672
00:36:26,040 --> 00:36:27,240
and left the base hospital

673
00:36:27,240 --> 00:36:28,600
riding his own motorcycle.

674
00:36:28,600 --> 00:36:29,400
This fact

675
00:36:29,400 --> 00:36:31,400
can be verified by the guards at the checkpoint.

676
00:36:31,400 --> 00:36:32,400
This way,

677
00:36:32,400 --> 00:36:34,400
the theory that the base hospital

678
00:36:34,400 --> 00:36:36,120
was the primary scene of Inoue Kamakura's death

679
00:36:36,120 --> 00:36:37,360
becomes invalid.

680
00:36:40,400 --> 00:36:41,840
So the Special Police Unit

681
00:36:41,840 --> 00:36:42,680
will soon trace

682
00:36:42,680 --> 00:36:43,880
to Ju'er?

683
00:36:43,880 --> 00:36:44,680
Yes.

684
00:36:45,320 --> 00:36:45,840
Ju'er,

685
00:36:46,480 --> 00:36:48,480
someone will definitely come to question you tomorrow.

686
00:36:48,480 --> 00:36:49,720
But if the person questioning you

687
00:36:49,720 --> 00:36:51,000
isn't Oshima Hiroshi himself

688
00:36:51,000 --> 00:36:52,640
but one of his officers,

689
00:36:52,640 --> 00:36:53,400
then we're

690
00:36:53,400 --> 00:36:54,720
halfway to success.

691
00:36:55,840 --> 00:36:56,720
But

692
00:36:57,560 --> 00:36:59,760
if Japanese people come to question me,

693
00:37:00,160 --> 00:37:01,600
what should I say?

694
00:37:01,800 --> 00:37:02,320
That's why it's best

695
00:37:02,320 --> 00:37:04,080
if Dr. Ozu is present

696
00:37:04,080 --> 00:37:05,600
when they question you.

697
00:37:05,600 --> 00:37:06,400
His testimony

698
00:37:06,400 --> 00:37:08,080
will be very helpful to you.

699
00:37:08,720 --> 00:37:10,160
Dr. Ozu.

700
00:37:11,760 --> 00:37:12,960
Don't be afraid, Ju'er.

701
00:37:12,960 --> 00:37:13,360
How about this,

702
00:37:13,360 --> 00:37:14,280
I'll go to the hospital tomorrow too.

703
00:37:14,280 --> 00:37:15,360
You can't go.

704
00:37:15,360 --> 00:37:16,360
If you go,

705
00:37:16,360 --> 00:37:18,520
it would be like announcing our guilt.

706
00:37:20,400 --> 00:37:21,000
What about you?

707
00:37:21,000 --> 00:37:22,080
I will go.

708
00:37:22,080 --> 00:37:22,720
I'll bring

709
00:37:22,720 --> 00:37:24,720
officers from the anti-aircraft artillery unit with me.

710
00:37:24,720 --> 00:37:26,120
In the Huangyang Mountain battle,

711
00:37:26,120 --> 00:37:27,400
many soldiers from the anti-aircraft unit

712
00:37:27,400 --> 00:37:28,560
were wounded.

713
00:37:28,560 --> 00:37:29,120
So it makes sense

714
00:37:29,120 --> 00:37:30,880
for me to visit and comfort them.

715
00:37:30,880 --> 00:37:31,680
Won't this attract

716
00:37:31,680 --> 00:37:33,360
the attention of the Special Police Unit?

717
00:37:33,360 --> 00:37:34,960
That's exactly what I want.

718
00:37:34,960 --> 00:37:35,800
To draw

719
00:37:35,800 --> 00:37:37,080
all their attention to me.

720
00:37:37,080 --> 00:37:37,960
This way,

721
00:37:37,960 --> 00:37:39,360
it will reduce their focus

722
00:37:39,360 --> 00:37:40,760
on the Major and Ju'er.

723
00:37:43,400 --> 00:37:44,240
Ju'er,

724
00:37:44,920 --> 00:37:46,920
did you remember everything I said?

725
00:38:00,920 --> 00:38:02,840
You should do it like this,

726
00:38:02,840 --> 00:38:04,120
you idiot.

727
00:38:05,200 --> 00:38:09,840
Are you out of your mind?

728
00:38:09,840 --> 00:38:10,840
I'm sorry,

729
00:38:11,240 --> 00:38:13,300
I can't even handle this simple task.

730
00:38:14,640 --> 00:38:16,300
You should place it like this.

731
00:38:19,960 --> 00:38:21,360
Do you know that Inoue is dead?

732
00:38:21,360 --> 00:38:22,360
I'm sorry.

733
00:38:22,360 --> 00:38:24,090
What on earth are you thinking?

734
00:38:24,920 --> 00:38:26,650
What on earth are you thinking?

735
00:38:26,880 --> 00:38:28,410
Captain, please calm down.

736
00:38:29,880 --> 00:38:30,760
Go now!

737
00:38:31,040 --> 00:38:32,040
Go now!

738
00:38:32,520 --> 00:38:33,040
Yes.

739
00:38:44,880 --> 00:38:46,120
Captain,

740
00:38:46,120 --> 00:38:47,400
get some rest.

741
00:38:48,400 --> 00:38:49,760
Sasaki.

742
00:38:56,560 --> 00:38:58,560
What do you think of these photos?

743
00:39:01,840 --> 00:39:03,500
It's absolutely impossible.

744
00:39:06,000 --> 00:39:10,160
One person couldn't have done this alone.

745
00:39:13,560 --> 00:39:18,400
How did it come to this?

746
00:39:22,640 --> 00:39:23,960
Sasaki.

747
00:39:26,520 --> 00:39:28,600
This is our most dangerous moment.

748
00:39:30,800 --> 00:39:32,080
We must maintain

749
00:39:32,080 --> 00:39:33,920
the highest level of vigilance.

750
00:40:21,520 --> 00:40:23,080
What are you doing?

751
00:40:24,360 --> 00:40:25,280
Stop drinking.

752
00:40:25,760 --> 00:40:27,760
Will drinking more solve anything?

753
00:40:29,640 --> 00:40:31,040
Just leave me alone.

754
00:40:32,000 --> 00:40:33,000
Father.

755
00:40:35,000 --> 00:40:36,880
I know why you're troubled.

756
00:40:38,800 --> 00:40:40,480
Listen to me just once.

757
00:40:41,320 --> 00:40:43,250
Don't go down the wrong path again.

758
00:40:44,040 --> 00:40:46,200
Do you think I want to make mistakes?

759
00:40:47,920 --> 00:40:49,850
I'm afraid something will happen.

760
00:40:50,960 --> 00:40:52,520
Just like last time.

761
00:40:53,760 --> 00:40:55,560
If that happens,

762
00:40:55,960 --> 00:40:57,640
how could we father and daughter

763
00:40:57,640 --> 00:40:59,480
show our faces on this island anymore?

764
00:40:59,480 --> 00:41:00,960
I would become

765
00:41:02,960 --> 00:41:05,720
a sinner for all eternity.

766
00:41:08,120 --> 00:41:09,600
Then don't go again.

767
00:41:10,400 --> 00:41:11,640
I don't want to go.

768
00:41:14,000 --> 00:41:15,880
But will the Japanese let me be?

769
00:41:20,720 --> 00:41:21,880
Ju'er.

770
00:41:23,520 --> 00:41:25,120
Go back to your room and rest.

771
00:41:26,480 --> 00:41:28,340
Let me have some quiet time alone.

772
00:41:33,080 --> 00:41:33,800
Mm.

773
00:41:34,240 --> 00:41:35,240
Go on.

774
00:42:08,600 --> 00:42:09,760
Captain Inoue

775
00:42:09,760 --> 00:42:11,960
He must have died before

776
00:42:12,120 --> 00:42:14,200
